Sportpesa, the leading betting firm in the region has announced that the SportPesa Mega Jackpot worth Sh230,742,881/= has been won. The announcement made on their social media confirms that the jackpot amount which is the biggest ever in Kenya has a winner. This follows a live broadcast that was done live on KTN Home and KBC at 12:45PM on Tuesday after game number 11: Troyes vs Dijon was postponed. In accordance to the Terms and Conditions, the company conducted a Public Draw to determine the outcome of this game and fully result the Mega Jackpot. The winner who will be announced shortly predicted the outcome as was published from the public draw.